
A girl wanted a ring. But the boy gave her a teddy bear instead. In anger, the girl threw the bear onto the street. The boy ran to get it, but was hit by a car.
At the boy's funeral, the girl sat and hugged the bear. She felt something poke her from the inside of the bear. So, she inspected it. Know what she found inside the teddy bear? A ring and a note that said, "Will you marry me?"